\
The board outlines the different stages of the project, and can be accessed here\outl0\strokewidth0 : https://trello.com/invite/b/69afe331de711564b48975f9/ATTI8d86225d06b4171e4a21bda89a97a2137E17C9B9/crime-data-eda\
