\cf0 \ul Project Folder Structure\ulnone \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 All project files are stored within the same folder, allowing the notebooks to use relative file paths when loading datasets. This ensures that the project can be run on another system without needing to modify file paths.\
The folder contains the following key components:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 CrimeDataProject/\
\
- CrimeDataMetPolice/			# Original crime datasets for Metropolitan Police Service\
- CrimeDataAllForces/			# Original crime datasets for all forces considered (monthly folders)\
- population.csv				# Original population dataset\
\
- London_Boroughs_Geographic_Data/	# Geographic shapefiles used for London borough mapping\
\
- Preprocessing.ipynb				# Notebook for data cleaning and preparation\
- REPORT.ipynb				# Notebook containing exploratory data analysis\
\
- crime_all_forces_clean.csv			# Cleaned dataset used for analysis\
- population_by_police_force.csv		# Aggregated population dataset used for analysis\
\
- preprocessing_flowchart.png		# Workflow diagram for preprocessing\
- README.md				# Project documentation\
- Statement of Work				# PDF document regarding statement of work\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
