\cf0 \ul Geographic Data \'96 London Boroughs\ulnone \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Folder: London_Boroughs_Geographic_Data/\
https://gis-tfl.opendata.arcgis.com/datasets/c6fbef8d68424c5cbcdf842c16ed4562_48/explore\
This folder contains geographic shapefiles for London borough boundaries. These files were used during an earlier stage of the project when the analysis focused specifically on the Metropolitan Police Service dataset.\
The shapefiles allow crime data to be visualised geographically using borough boundaries. This made it possible to explore how crime patterns varied across different boroughs within London before expanding the analysis to multiple police forces.\
These files include standard shapefile components such as:\
