\cf0 Crime Dataset\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 File: crime_all_forces_clean.csv\
This dataset contains the cleaned and combined crime data used in the exploratory analysis. It includes crime records from the selected police forces over the specified time period.\
Metropolitan Crime dataset\
File: crime_metro_clean.csv\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 This dataset contains the cleaned and combined crime data achieved from the Metropolitan Police Service preprocessing and analysis. It includes street and outcome data.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Population Dataset\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 File: population_by_police_force.csv\
This dataset contains population totals aggregated by police force. The population data allows crime levels to be adjusted relative to population size, enabling the calculation of crimes per 1,000 residents.\
Population figures are derived from the 2021 UK Census (TS001 \'96 Number of usual residents).\
