\f0\b \cf0 \outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 Required Python Libraries\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf0 To run the notebooks in this project successfully, several Python libraries must be installed. These libraries are used for data manipulation, visualisation, and geographic mapping.\
If these packages are not already installed in your Python environment, they can be installed using pip.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \strokec5 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa321\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf0 \strokec3 Required Libraries\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf0 The project relies on the following libraries:\
- pandas - data manipulation and analysis\
- numpy - numerical operations\
matplotlib - data visualisation\
- seaborn - statistical visualisations\
- folium - interactive geographic maps\
- geopandas - geographic data processing\
- contextily - basemaps for spatial visualisations\
- shapely - geometric operations used by geopandas\
- IPython - used for rendering formatted outputs\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa321\partightenfactor0

