\cf0 This project provides an exploratory analysis of crime patterns across selected regions of the United Kingdom. By combining crime data, population data, and regional classifications, the analysis identifies patterns that may be relevant for evaluating the desirability of locations within residential property markets.\
The results of the exploratory analysis inform the selection of two police forces for further investigation, which will be explored in greater detail in the next stage of the project.\
